description: Amundi J.P. Morgan USD Emerging Markets Bond UCITS ETF DR - USD (C) seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the J.P. Morgan EMBI Global Diversified Select Index (the Index), and to minimize the tracking error between the net asset value of the Sub-Fund and the performance of the Index. The anticipated level of tracking error, under normal market conditions, is indicated in the prospectus of the Sub-Fund. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
